Records with Clive Wright<ref name=\"Progarchives\"/>\n* ''Little Windows'' (2010) Darla Records with Clive Wright<ref name=\"Progarchives\"/>\n* ''Nighthawks, Translucence and Drift Music'' 37-track, 3-CD digipak (2011) Edsel Records with John Foxx\n* ''Bordeaux'' (2011) Darla Records with Robin Guthrie<ref name=\"Progarchives\"/>\n* ''Winter Garden'' (2011) RareNoiseRecords with Robin Guthrie & Eraldo Bernocchi<ref name=\"Guthrie\"/>\n* ''In the Mist'' (2011) Darla Records<ref name=\"Progarchives\"/>\n* ''Bandits of Stature'' (2012) Darla Records, P Toyon Music (BMI), distributed in the US by Caroline Records, Inc.\n* ''Jane 1\u201311'' (2013) Darla Records\n* ''Wind in Lonely Fences 1970 \u2013 2011'' 18-track, 2-CD digipak (2013) All Saints Records with Cocteau Twins and Robin Guthrie, John Foxx, & Brian Eno\n* ''Buddbox'' anthology box set containing 7 hard-to-find and critically acclaimed albums (2013) All Saints Records\n* \"Buddbox Sampler\" Limited edition 15-track promo sampler for the 7 CD Buddbox anthology box set (2013) All Saints Records\n* ''Jane 12\u201321'' (2014) Darla Records\n* ''[[White Bird in a Blizzard]]'' (2014) Lakeshore Records with Robin Guthrie<ref name=\"Guthrie\"/>\n\n==See also==\n* [[Brian Eno]]\n* [[Experimental music]]\n*[[List of ambient music artists]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://haroldbudd.com/ Harold Budd] Home page\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20091009012653/http://www.newalbion.com/artists/buddh/index.htm New Albion Records] Harold Budd page\n* [http://www.samadhisound.com/haroldbudd/ Samadhisound] Harold Budd page\n* [http://www.sleepbot.com/ambience/page/budd.html Ambience for the Masses] Harold Budd page\n* [https://pages.bookstellyouwhy.com/harold-budd Books Tell You Why] Harold Budd: His Life & Works\n* [http://www.soundonsound.com/sos/1997_articles/jan97/haroldbudd.html Harold Budd: American Vision] article from Sound on Sound magazine\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/200705130